// Background ::

// What are Arduinos?
// Arduinos are open-source micro-controllers designed to allow for anyone to build and control circuits easily
// Arduinos are controlled through the Arduino IDE, which can be downloaded for free from the Arduino site.

// Guide ::

1.0- Download Arduino Libraries

> sudo apt-get install arduino

